ComicInfo.Summary:
Rubber Guns, Chapter 2: The Rubber Guns try to rescue Charisma from the yacht.
Murder Society, Chapter 1 - A Well Tailored Murder: A new member of the Murder Society tells how he murdered his partner.
The Once and Future Tarzan, Chapter 9: The group struggles to get all aboard the submarine.
Brooklyn Blood, Chapter 10: O'Connor is freaking out after the medium told him he was the killer's next target.
Chase the Lady, Chapter 11: Rachel goes to the kitchen.
Death Rides a Bullet: Chapter 02: The Mayor unleashes his plan to stop the Black Sinister.
